---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Payroll & HR Advisory | ARM Management"
  description="Global payroll strategy, multi-country payroll compliance, international assignment planning, and HR advisory across all operating jurisdictions."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521791136064-7986c2920216?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Payroll &amp; HR</span>
      <h1>Payroll &amp; HR Advisory</h1>
      <p>Multi-country payroll compliance and workforce strategy across every jurisdiction you employ in.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">What We Do</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">International Payroll Without the Exposure</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Running payroll across multiple countries is one of the most compliance-intensive activities an international business undertakes. Employment law, social security contributions, income tax withholding, benefits requirements, and termination rules vary dramatically by jurisdiction — and non-compliance exposes both the business and its directors to significant legal and financial risk.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">ARM Management provides strategic advisory on global payroll structure, multi-country payroll compliance, international assignment planning, and workforce strategy — coordinated across all your operating jurisdictions through a single senior relationship.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Services</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What We Advise On</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Global Payroll Strategy</h3>
          <p>Designing optimal payroll structures for international workforces — employer of record arrangements, local entity payroll, and contractor management frameworks that balance compliance, cost, and flexibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Multi-Country Payroll Compliance</h3>
          <p>Ensuring accurate calculation, withholding, and reporting of payroll taxes, social security contributions, and mandatory benefits across all jurisdictions where you have employees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>International Assignment Planning</h3>
          <p>Structuring secondments, expatriate assignments, and cross-border transfers with tax efficiency, legal compliance, and employee fairness — including hypothetical tax calculations and net pay equalisation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Shadow Payroll</h3>
          <p>Managing shadow payroll obligations for internationally mobile employees to ensure correct tax reporting in both home and host countries, preventing double taxation and compliance failures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Employment Contract Review</h3>
          <p>Reviewing and advising on employment contracts across jurisdictions to ensure compliance with local mandatory requirements while protecting the business's commercial interests.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>HR Compliance Advisory</h3>
          <p>Advising on mandatory HR policies, working time regulations, leave entitlements, data protection obligations, and termination procedures across all operating jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">The ARM Approach</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">Strategy Before Compliance.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78)">Most payroll providers process transactions. ARM Management starts upstream: we advise on how your international workforce should be structured before addressing how it should be administered. The right structure significantly reduces compliance cost, tax exposure, and the risk of inadvertently creating permanent establishments or triggering unexpected employer obligations in new jurisdictions.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Structure First</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Before processing a single payslip, we assess whether your employment structure is optimal. The wrong structure creates liabilities that payroll processing alone cannot fix.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Director-Level Risk Awareness</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Payroll non-compliance creates personal liability for directors in many jurisdictions. We ensure you understand what you are signing off on in each country.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Coordinated Local Networks</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We work with vetted employment law and payroll specialists in each jurisdiction — coordinated through a single ARM relationship so nothing falls between advisors.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Expansion Advisory</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Before you hire in a new country, we assess the employment law implications, required registrations, cost of employment, and optimal engagement structure.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Where We Advise</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="reveal" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:32px">
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">European Union</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">All EU member states plus UK and Switzerland. Social security, income tax withholding, statutory benefits, Works Council obligations.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">GCC &amp; Middle East</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">UAE WPS-compliant payroll, GPSSA and GOSI contributions, end-of-service gratuity, and free zone employment rules.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Asia Pacific</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Singapore CPF, Hong Kong MPF, Malaysia EPF and SOCSO, India PF and ESI, and other APAC mandatory contributions.</p></div>
        <div style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">Latin America</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Mexico IMSS, Colombia PILA, Brazil eSocial and FGTS, Chile AFP, and other LatAm mandatory social contributions.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Related Guides</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Go Deeper</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/uae-employment-payroll" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">UAE · Payroll</span>
          <h3>UAE Employment &amp; Payroll</h3>
          <p>End-of-service gratuity, the Wage Protection System, the 2026 salary-date rule, Emiratisation and leave.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read the guide →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">All Insights</span>
          <h3>Browse the Guide Library</h3>
          <p>Jurisdiction and regulatory guides across the markets ARM advises in — reviewed and cited.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">View all →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Discuss Your Global Workforce</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Tell us where you employ, what structures you currently have in place, and where you are expanding. We will identify the risks and design a compliant, efficient solution.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/insights" class="btn-secondary">Read Our Insights</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
